        "productTagline": "<p>\n    Virtual Clinical Surveillance for Hospital and System-Wide Monitoring\n</p>",
        "bodyCopy": "<p>\n    Hospitals and health systems use the PeraWatch virtual surveillance platform for system-wide identification of patient deterioration and bed management by decentralized, âcommand centerâ clinicians.\n</p>\n<p>\n    PeraWatch provides an added layer of patient safety that extends a care teamâs reach across multiple units and facilities. The software platform leverages the Rothman Index (RI) to assimilate disparate clinical data through configurable surveillance views. With this information, decentralized clinicians can garner an acute awareness of current patient condition and promote appropriate clinical actions to decrease âreactiveâ rapid response and code situations, and drive improvements in care efficiency and effectiveness. Clinicians can also leverage the surveillance platform to manage patient flow and bed utilization within the hospital and across the system.\n</p>",
        "productHighlights": "<p>\n    - Hospital and system-wide remote monitoring\n</p>\n<p>\n    - Real-time clinical surveillance and bed management\n</p>\n<p>\n    - All patient populations and care settings, including med/surg and ICU units\n</p>\n<p>\n    - Configuration and dashboards based on hospital and unit assignments\n</p>\n<p>\n    - Navigation through assigned patients for clinical status awareness and detail drill down\n</p>",
        "productScreengrabs": null,
        "title": "PeraWatch",
        "slug": "perawatch"
      }
