        "jobPurpose": "<p>\n    The Clinical Adoption Specialist will develop an understanding of the clientâs clinical improvement initiatives in order to support their clinical adoption goals for PeraHealth. The Specialist will assess processes and analyze data to develop the insights required to guide clients to successful clinical deployment. Additionally, this resource will work internally with the PeraHealth services team to implement and deploy PeraHealth solutions in a timely manner.\n</p>",
        "location": "<p>\n    Charlotte, NC\n</p>",
        "travelExpectation": "<p>\n    50%\n</p>",
        "jobResponsibilities": "<ol>\n    <li>Manage the clinical deployment process and adoption of PeraHealth tools.\n    </li>\n    <li>Develop and foster relationships with clientsâ clinical stakeholders and leadership.\n    </li>\n    <li>Effectively communicate and escalate barriers to adoption.\n    </li>\n    <li>Provide guidance to client from discovery and analysis through deployment and monitoring phases of implementation.\n    </li>\n    <li>Analyze clinical data to identify client operational opportunities and internal product development.\n    </li>\n    <li>Perform client operational workflow and systems assessments.\n    </li>\n    <li>Assist client in designing workable process solutions while providing education on PeraHealth tools.\n    </li>\n    <li>Assist in product testing and technical validation of new or modified systems.\n    </li>\n</ol>",
        "qualifications": "<ol>\n    <li>Strong critical thinking and analysis skills with the ability to break down complex problems into manageable tasks.\n    </li>\n    <li>Minimum of a four year degree (BS, MBA, MHA, etc.) and clinical licensure. For example RN, PA, PT, RPH, RT.\n    </li>\n    <li>3 years of work experience in clinical hospital setting.\n    </li>\n    <li>Minimum of two years of involvement in clinical process improvement initiatives.\n    </li>\n    <li>Understanding of software implementation lifecycle.\n    </li>\n    <li>Competence in data analysis, spreadsheet creation, data collection and entry.\n    </li>\n    <li>Proven capability with Microsoft Office Suite.\n    </li>\n    <li>Strong verbal and written communication skills.\n    </li>\n    <li>Excellent organizational and planning skills.\n    </li>\n    <li>Ability to work on multiple projects with multiple deadlines.\n    </li>\n    <li>2-4 years of consulting experience preferred.\n    </li>\n</ol>",
        "additionalSkills": "",
