        "travelExpectation": "<p>\n    Minimal\n</p>",
        "jobResponsibilities": "<ul>\n    <li>Manage and execute campaigns to prospect, qualify and develop sales-ready leads through targeted outbound calling and emailing.\n    </li>\n    <li>Communicate with prospects, including C-suite executives and hospital leadership using effective outreach methods via email and phone.\n    </li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n    <li>Respond to inbound requests and schedule product/solutions presentations.\n    </li>\n    <li>Schedule sales meetings and appointments for assigned sales executives with prospects to achieve weekly and monthly goals.\n    </li>\n    <li>Prepare background material and market research in preparation for all sales meetings and appointments.\n    </li>\n    <li>Manage post-sales meeting follow such as finalizing client agreements, scheduling follow up calls and assisting with other business activities.\n    </li>\n    <li>Maintain internal database to track key performance metrics and marketing activities (Salesforce.com).\n    </li>\n    <li>Develop knowledge in PeraHealthâs solutions and products, and industry trends.\n    </li>\n    <li>Create a strategic outreach plan with assigned sales executives to target prospects through market segmentation.\n    </li>\n    <li>Collaborate with the Product team to share market intelligence and customer feedback to help guide future product or feature development that drives customer acquisition and retention\n    </li>\n</ul>",
        "qualifications": "<ul>\n    <li>Bachelorâs Degree\n    </li>\n    <li>1-2 years experience as an inside sales representative preferably in a B2B and healthcare environment\n    </li>\n    <li>Excellent organizational, presentation, and communication skills (written and verbal)\n    </li>\n    <li>Ability to work independently as well as collaborate with teams to maximize results\n    </li>\n    <li>Experience analyzing product, customer and market dynamics to determine greatest opportunities for product sales and differentiation opportunities\n    </li>\n    <li>Proficiency with Word, Excel, and PowerPoint for MAC\n    </li>\n    <li>Ability to communicate by e-mail and phone with senior executives\n    </li>\n    <li>Proven experience managing multiple, competing priorities while working towards an established goal\n    </li>\n    <li>Ability to overcome challenges or obstacles in the moment\n    </li>\n    <li>Strong follow up and persuasive skills\n    </li>\n    <li>Confident, assertive self-starter who is extremely organized and goal driven\n    </li>\n    <li>Must possess at least two of the following:\n        <ul>\n            <li>Sales experience\n            </li>\n            <li>Customer service experience\n            </li>\n            <li>Experience working in a marketing or sales team environment\n            </li>\n            <li>Experience in an office setting\n            </li>\n        </ul>\n    </li>\n</ul>",
