        "leadershipRole": "<p>\n    Senior Vice President, Marketing and Product Strategy\n</p>",
        "quotefromLeader": "<p>\n    âThere are few times you have the opportunity to join something that will make a significant difference in peopleâs lives. PeraHealthâs unique combination of technology, data, and partnership with providers enables us to transform how care is provided today.â\n</p>",
        "leadershipBio": "<p>\n    Meredith comes to PeraHealth with over fifteen years experience working with providers, payers, manufacturers and academia. Over the last three years she has been an advisor to start-ups and small companies, assisting with their marketing and growth plans. Prior to that, Meredith worked for Johnson &amp; Johnson as a Worldwide Marketing Manager, directing global marketing activities from a tactical and strategic standpoint for one of their business lines. While at J&amp;J, she was selected to join their threeâyear leadership program. Prior to J&amp;J, Meredith spent five years in healthcare management consulting leading quality improvement, cost reduction and revenue enhancements projects for multiple healthcare systems. Meredith began her healthcare career performing early stage oncology and cell biology research at Duke University.\n</p>\n<p>\n    Meredith has her MBA from Harvard Business School and her BA from Princeton University.\n</p>",
