        "leadershipBio": "<p>\n    Pamela is a 30-year veteran sales executive with a history of success in a start-up healthcare environment.\n</p>\n<p>\n    Before joining PeraHealth in September 2012, Pam was health system sales leader for the Informatics division of Premier Inc. She also directed sales operations for a newly acquired Premier company, SafetySurveillor. Prior to Premier, Pam was vice president of sales for CareScience, vice president of sales operations and area vice president for MediServe Information Systems.\n</p>\n<p>\n    Pamâs clinical experience as a registered Respiratory care practitioner included critical care, pediatric, cardiac, burn ICU, emergency medicine, and home care for ventilator dependent children and adults. She received her Respiratory degree at SUNY Upstate Medical Center and holds a Bachelors Degree from State University of New York in Healthcare Services.\n</p>",
