        "productTagline": "<p>\n    Real-time Clinical Surveillance Across Patient Populations and Care Settings\n</p>",
        "bodyCopy": "<p>\n    PeraTrend is a predictive warning system that alerts clinicians to subtle, potentially life-threatening deterioration through a visual representation of a patientâs condition. Leveraging the Rothman Index (RI), PeraTrend can be accessed through integration with a providerâs electronic health record (EHR) of choice, as well as through a web-based URL which can be displayed on a nursing unit board. PeraTrend is leveraged for nursing unit level or across the house clinical surveillance.\n</p>",
        "productHighlights": "<p>\n    - Real-time, clinical surveillance\n</p>\n<p>\n    - All patient populations and care settings\n</p>\n<p>\n    - Detects deterioration earlier, often with &amp;gt;24hrs warning, and minimal false alerts\n</p>\n<p>\n    - Facilitates communication during shift changes and handoffs\n</p>\n<p>\n    - Automatically calculates from existing EHR data and integrates with all major EHR vendors\n</p>",
        "productScreengrabs": null,
        "title": "PeraTrend",
        "slug": "peratrend"
