        "productTagline": "<p>\n    Mobile Clinical Surveillance for Proactive Rapid Response\n</p>",
        "bodyCopy": "<p>\n    PeraMobile enables proactive rapid response teams to identify patients at risk for deterioration by engaging and empowering clinicians with real-time context-based mobile information for improved clinical decision making. On-the-move clinicians can easily track patients through a mobile device who<a></a>have achieved an organizationally-determined limit. Organizational configuration options enable clinical leaders to determine when the clinical response team is notified, through a push notification, reducing alarm fatigue and increasing trust in the system.\n</p>",
        "productHighlights": "<p>\n    - Enable rapid response teams to transition from a reactive to a proactive care model\n</p>\n<p>\n    - Mobile notification of patient deterioration\n</p>\n<p>\n    - Custom deterioration thresholds by organization\n</p>\n<p>\n    - Create individualized custom watchlists to monitor concerning patients\n</p>\n<p>\n    - Leverage optional filters such as new admissions or recent transfers out of critical care areas\n</p>",
