        "articleSummary": "<p>\n    77 lives: Thatâs how many patients Houston Methodist Hospital saved over a nine-month period in 2014 and 2015 after deploying an early warning system that continuously scans the electronic health record (EHR) to identify patients whose condition is deteriorating.\n</p>",
        "publication": "<p>\n    Health Data Management\n</p>",
        "publicationDate": "2016-03-24",
        "sourceLink": "<p>\n    <a href=\"http://www.healthdatamanagement.com/news/houston-methodist-uses-data-assessments-in-its-ehr-to-save-lives?reading_list=%5B'00000153-a4f8-dba7-afd7-a7fdb8f40000','00000153-a4ec-dba7-afd7-a7fd8d790000','00000153-a33f-d098-a37b-f73f83de0000','00000153-a86f-d098-a37b-fe6fe61f0000','00000153-a86d-d098-a37b-fe6df80a0000','00000153-a868-d098-a37b-fe69f5ca0000','00000153-a4da-d098-a37b-f6fb3f180000'%5D\" target=\"_blank\">Read More</a>\n</p>",
